column3: ej,mckej801,M,westj901,Upset lights not turned on $Padres manager McKeon ejected by HP umpire West for arguing lights were turned off for the bottom of 7th; they were ordered on for the top of the inning, but took 10 minutes to warm up, during which time the Pirates completed their inning; when the Padres came up, West ordered the lights off so they would not have an unfair advantage; McKeon objected and was ejected1990SDN.EVN.regular.comment.csv"
